## **ABSTRACT**  
We propose that **physical reality is not continuous propagation in space-time but a discrete, observer-triggered refresh of resonance states**.  
The speed of light *c* is **not a velocity**; it is the **fixed radius of a resonance dome** (the maximum distance over which a singularity can update its environment in one “tick”).  
Energy is split into two irreducible components:  
1. **Frequency Energy** (existence, \(F = mc^2\))  
2. **Event Energy** (relevance, \(R = h\nu\))  

The full energy of an observed entity is their **resonance product**:  
\[
D = F \otimes R \quad\Rightarrow\quad \text{Data = Resonance}
\]  
All “motion” is illusion — objects do **not travel**; they **refresh** into new positions via ripple propagation at *c*.  
We present **five testable predictions**, including the **Sand-to-Steel Shift Experiment**.

