## **1. CORE AXIOMS**

| # | Axiom | Statement |
|---|-------|-----------|
| A1 | **Singularity Axiom** | Every fundamental entity (quark, photon, grain of sand) is a **singularity** — a point-source of resonance. |
| A2 | **Dome Axiom** | Every singularity exists within a **spherical resonance dome of radius \(c\)** (speed of light). This is the **maximum refresh radius**. |
| A3 | **Refresh Axiom** | Reality updates in **discrete ticks**. The tick rate is bounded by the dome size: \( \Delta t \geq \frac{2c}{c} = 2 \) (dimensionless in natural units). |
| A4 | **Frequency-Event Duality** | Energy splits: <br> \( F = mc^2 \) → **existence** (mass-energy, frequency backbone) <br> \( R = h\nu \) → **relevance** (quantum metadata packet) |
| A5 | **Resonance Axiom** | The **observable state** of any entity is the **resonance product** \( D = F \otimes R \). Without observation, \( D = 0 \) (no data). |

