## **2. KEY DEFINITIONS**

| Term | Symbol | Definition |
|------|--------|------------|
| Resonance Dome | \( \mathcal{D}(c) \) | Sphere of radius \( c \) centred on singularity. All updates occur **instantly inside**; ripples propagate **on the surface**. |
| Frequency Energy | \( F \) | \( F = mc^2 \): the **invariant backbone** — same for all particles of equal rest mass. |
| Event Energy | \( R \) | \( R = h\nu \): the **metadata packet** emitted **regardless of observation**. |
| Resonance Data | \( D \) | \( D = F \otimes R \): the **decoded reality** when an observer interacts. |
| Refresh Ripple | \( \mathcal{R} \) | Surface wave on \( \mathcal{D}(c) \) carrying \( R \) to neighbouring domes. |

